    <so:textual_span>For genetic confirmation, a fin clip stored in 96% ethanol, was digested with Proteinase K in a lysis buffer (10 mM Tris, 400 mM NaCl, 2 mM EDTA, 1% SDS) at 55</so:textual_span>
