    <so:sentence_text>For genetic confirmation, a fin clip stored in 96% ethanol, was digested with Proteinase K in a lysis buffer (10 mM Tris, 400 mM NaCl, 2 mM EDTA, 1% SDS) at 55°C and total DNA was extracted according to Sambrook et al. (1989).</so:sentence_text>
