    <so:description>A dynamic web page is a web page constructed at runtime (during software execution), as opposed to a static web page, delivered as it is stored. A server-side dynamic web page is a web page whose construction is controlled by an application server processing server-side scripts.</so:description>
    <so:wikipedia_url>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=1697881</so:wikipedia_url>
  </rdf:Description>
